# Template可将字符串的格式固定下来，重复利用;让开发人员可以分别考虑字符串的格式和其内容，减轻了开发人员的压力。
# Template是Python string模板中定义的一种字符串类型
# 用途：用于字符串替换操作
# 默认的定界符：$
# https://docs.python.org/2.4/lib/node109.html

from string import Template

myString = Template('$who likes $what')
print(myString.substitute(who='Bob', what='KFC.'))

# "${identifier}" is equivalent to "$identifier".
myString = Template('${who} likes $what')
print(myString.substitute(who='Bob', what='KFC.'))


myString = Template('$$Who likes $what')
print(myString.substitute(who='Bob', what='KFC.'))

